{"type": "article", "id": 22807, "title": "住一间这样的度假木屋，大人与小孩各有空间", "description": "小房间可以参考的空间布局", "date": "2016-02-25T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 373, "name": "俄罗斯"}, {"id": 14211, "name": "周末"}, {"id": 5449, "name": "小孩"}, {"id": 23926, "name": "嬉戏"}, {"id": 19098, "name": "木屋"}, {"id": 23927, "name": "布局"}, {"id": 971, "name": "空间"}], "category": 17, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 209, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021139494pyD37q2WiUtZzck.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>在俄罗斯，很多家庭每逢周末就会去他们在城郊以及乡村边缘的别墅度假，说是别墅，其实有些就是一间俄式的传统小木屋 summer house。</p>\n<p class=\"\">但对于有小孩的家庭来说，问题就来了，本来是家长们梦想在一周的忙碌工作之后好好休息、放松一下的日子。小孩子们却总是醒得很早开始嬉戏玩耍，让人根本没办法睡个懒觉。</p>\n<p class=\"\">为了让大人们在这样的单间 summer house 里有更多的时间呆在床上、尽量不被打扰，俄罗斯事务所 Ruetemple 就为他们的客户重新设计了小木屋的内部空间布局。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021139443VthLN5wTubX0Pa2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113945SKQ9WZjPeBFTV740.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">建筑师在原本的房屋内增添了两层为孩子准备的玩耍空间，为此建了一个完整的木质结构。包括底层的内嵌软垫的床，在床铺上面两层高出的空间和连接的木质楼梯。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113945ahK5Uj4mlvLYM97s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">底层的空间属于家长，巨大的软垫不管是休息还是看看电视都很舒适。全身镜打开，还有一个秘密房间。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113946Fg1N75huCWYxeEmB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113946HC2SOqTJAtEejkin.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">侧面的楼梯通往夹层，空缺处都设置了高质量的防护网，完全不用担心孩子跑来跑去不安全。二层软垫供孩子休息，再往上则还有一个玩具间。看起来那个小小的玩具间几面都用上了木板，或许还有隔音的功能。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113947aTZkSgPKUR0ispL1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05591398\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113947Ic3T4dQRgtbjUPWJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05137845\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113948FiLvfSBARuZ0qnb6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113948LTpKWgiUn5lJA2et.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021139493ReHpoVPvbM6fFtn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2016/02/22/this-parents-bedroom-also-has-a-play-area-for-the-kids/\">Contemporist</a></p>\n\n"}